title: Google\Cloud\AutoMl\V1beta1\Float64Stats
name: Float64Stats
description:
The data statistics of a series of FLOAT64 values.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.automl.v1beta1.Float64Stats

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.quantiles
params.description: Ordered from 0 to k k-quantile values of the data series of n values. The value at index i is, approximately, the i*n/k-th smallest value in the series; for i = 0 and i = k these are, respectively, the min and max values.

params.name: data.histogram_buckets
params.description: Histogram buckets of the data series. Sorted by the min value of the bucket, ascendingly, and the number of the buckets is dynamically generated. The buckets are non-overlapping and completely cover whole FLOAT64 range with min of first bucket being "-Infinity", and max of the last one being "Infinity".
